834
00:51:14,960 --> 00:51:17,320
Then again,
maybe they hadn't forgotten...

835
00:51:17,360 --> 00:51:19,360
or maybe they were trying
to forget.

836
00:51:19,400 --> 00:51:20,600
Maybe there was a reason...

837
00:51:20,640 --> 00:51:22,680
