915
00:56:40,640 --> 00:56:42,760
JEFF: Ow!
Gloria, where are the Q-tips?

916
00:56:42,800 --> 00:56:44,040
GLORlA: We don't have any.

917
00:56:44,080 --> 00:56:46,200
JEFF: You can't find anything
in here!

918
00:56:46,240 --> 00:56:49,400
