for Wild Turkey.

937
00:57:44,600 --> 00:57:47,720
He went on and on about
the old Billy Sullivan case.

938
00:57:47,760 --> 00:57:49,800
Said he'd have solved it
20 years ago...

939
00:57:49,840 --> 00:57:52,000
if he'd had a court order
and a bulldozer.

940
00:57:52,040 --> 00:57:53,520
The way he figured it...

941
00:57:53,560 --> 00:57:55,920
