at that ranch that Ames owns...

942
00:57:55,960 --> 00:57:57,840
the one nobody goes near.

943
00:57:57,880 --> 00:57:59,760
JEFF: That's when I got
the idea to call Mel.

944
00:57:59,800 --> 00:58:01,680
Get her to let me stay
at the ranch house...

945
00:58:01,720 --> 00:58:03,120
so I could look for the body.

946
00:58:03,160 --> 00:58:05,960
