987
01:00:32,160 --> 01:00:34,800
GLORlA: I know better, too.

988
01:00:49,920 --> 01:00:52,440
Jesus Christ.

989
01:01:14,880 --> 01:01:17,920
Sure you wanna be
in this line of work, huh?

990
01:01:22,520 --> 01:01:24,400
Jack, it's me.

991
01:01:24,440 --> 01:01:27,960
What do you think that house
of yours is worth?

992
01:01:28,000 --> 01:01:32,080
