stand bail for me tonight.

993
01:01:32,120 --> 01:01:34,480
And, Jack, one other thing.

994
01:01:34,520 --> 01:01:38,080
I am fucking fed up
working for you.

995
01:01:39,200 --> 01:01:40,720
[Exhales]

996
01:01:40,760 --> 01:01:42,600
